extCardText:

• 8 Pokemon TCG: Sun & Moon - Cosmic Eclipse booster packs
• 65 card sleeves featuring Arceus & Dialga & Palkia
• 45 Pokémon TCG Energy cards

• A code card for the Pokemon Trading Card Game Online
